Title: Ecobug
Description: Tired of increasing amounts of pollution and the impact of green house effect on your holiday plans? Want to live a greener life? Want to help preserve a healthy and safe planet for your children? Ecobug is an exciting new appliaction helping you to do exactly that. Star using it's tracker to check how much CO2 and trees you save by walking instead of driving. Take a look at the daily tips on how to make your life-style more enviromentaly friendly. Check your progress by taking part in our Ecobug quiz. Help us save the planet!
Promo text (80 chars): EcoBug helps you save energy and live a greener life.
